fields.history_note:
References: 


The prints show the donor (b 06/1937) 11 years to adult,
with parents Vera & William Archibald Kempson & other fam
ily members (Vera Kempson, Doris Elmes & Jack Youens are
siblings, Archibald Kempson, Lawrence Elmes & Ella Youens
 their spouses; Mary Kempson, Peter Elmes & Sheila Youens
 their children; Mrs Youens is Vera, Doris & Jack's mother)
